==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Buck fever
<hw>Buck fever</hw>. <def>Intense excitement at the sight of deer or
other game, such as often unnerves a novice in hunting.</def>
<mark>[Colloq.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

